           ELSE
      *@원장조회에러일경우
      *@에러메세지 : 테이블 SELECT 오류입니다．
      *@조치메세지 : 전산업무담당자에게　문의바랍니다
              #ERROR CO-B3900009 CO-UKJL0036 CO-STAT-ERROR
           END-IF

      *@2.5 출력변수 MOVE
      *    채무자명
           MOVE XQJL1251-O-DBTRZ-NAME
             TO XDJL4027-O-DBTRZ-NAME

220324*    포괄신용관리한도가 0이 아니면(설정상태:설정)이면
           IF XQJL1251-O-MGT-CLAM NOT = ZERO
      *@       TE여신성최고한도2011.06.03추가
               COMPUTE XDJL4027-O-LNBZ-I-HGST-LIMT
                     = FUNCTION MAX(
                       XQJL1251-O-LNBZ-I-HGST-LIMT / 1000000, 0)
      *@       포괄신용공여한도
               COMPUTE XDJL4027-O-MGT-CLAM
                     = XQJL1251-O-MGT-CLAM / 1000000
      *@       최종승인　관리한도
      *@             = MIN(TE여신성최고한도，포괄신용공여한도)
               COMPUTE XDJL4027-O-LAST-INLS-LIMT
                     = FUNCTION MAX(
                       FUNCTION MIN(XQJL1251-O-LNBZ-I-HGST-LIMT,
                                    XQJL1251-O-MGT-CLAM) / 1000000, 0)
220324*@       기사용액 = MIN(사용액, 최종적용 포괄신용공여한도)
               COMPUTE XDJL4027-O-INLS-GRCR-LIMT-AUC
                     = FUNCTION MAX(
                       FUNCTION MIN(
                       XQJL1251-O-INLS-GRCR-LIMT-AUC / 1000000,
                       XDJL4027-O-LAST-INLS-LIMT), 0)
      *@       한도여유액＝최종승인　관리한도-기사용액
               COMPUTE XDJL4027-O-LIMT-SEXTR-AMT
                     = XDJL4027-O-LAST-INLS-LIMT
                     - XDJL4027-O-INLS-GRCR-LIMT-AUC
           END-IF

      *@   계열명
           MOVE XQJL1251-O-AFFLT-C-GROUP-NAME
             TO XDJL4027-O-AFFLT-C-GROUP-NAME
      *@   계열신용등급
           MOVE XQJL1251-O-INTNL-CV-GRD-DSTCD
             TO XDJL4027-O-INTNL-CV-GRD-DSTCD
      *@   기업신용등급
