             TO XDJL4027-O-INTNL-CV-GRD-DSTCD1
      *@   유효기일
           MOVE XQJL1251-O-MGT-LIMT-VALD-YMD
             TO XDJL4027-O-MGT-LIMT-VALD-YMD
      *@   업종명
           MOVE XQJL1251-O-STND-IDSTRY-CD-NAME
             TO XDJL4027-O-STND-IDSTRY-CD-NAME
