       S3300-QJL0272-CALL-RTN.

      *@   SQLIO OPEN
           PERFORM S3310-QJL0272-OPEN-RTN
              THRU S3310-QJL0272-OPEN-EXT

           MOVE  CO-CHA-Y
             TO  WK-BIT

      *@   SQLIO FETCH
           PERFORM UNTIL WK-BIT     = CO-CHA-N OR
                         WK-CUR-CNT = CO-MAX-CNT
      *@      SQLIO FETCH CALL
              PERFORM S3320-QJL0272-FETCH-RTN
                 THRU S3320-QJL0272-FETCH-EXT
           END-PERFORM

      *@   SQLIO CLOSE
           PERFORM S3330-QJL0272-CLOSE-RTN
