      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@ 포괄신용공여한도기업여신현황출력
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S6000-OUTPUT-SET-RTN.

      *@   OUTPUT
           PERFORM VARYING WK-I FROM 1 BY 1
                   UNTIL WK-I > DBSQL-SELECT-CNT

               ADD 1 TO WK-CUR-CNT

220324*@       기준년월일
               MOVE  XQJL0272-O-BASE-YMD(WK-I)
                 TO  XDJL4027-O-BASE-YMD(WK-CUR-CNT)

      *@       회계구분
               MOVE XQJL0272-O-ACCTG-DSTCD(WK-I)
                 TO XDJL4027-O-TE-ITEM-DSTIC1(WK-CUR-CNT)

      *@       상품코드
               MOVE  XQJL0272-O-PRDCT-CD(WK-I)
                 TO  XDJL4027-O-PRDCT-CD1(WK-CUR-CNT)

      *@       상품명
               MOVE  XQJL0272-O-PRDCT-NAME(WK-I)
                 TO  XDJL4027-O-PRDCT-NAME1(WK-CUR-CNT)

      *@       자산구분
               MOVE  XQJL0272-O-TE-ASST-DSTCD(WK-I)
                 TO  XDJL4027-O-TE-ASST-DSTCD1(WK-CUR-CNT)

      *@       명목액기준한도
               MOVE  XQJL0272-O-TTL-AMT-BASE-CLAM(WK-I)
                 TO  XDJL4027-O-TTL-AMT-BASE-CLAM1(WK-CUR-CNT)

      *@       명목액기준잔액
