                 TO  XDJL4027-O-TTL-AMT-BASE-BAL1(WK-CUR-CNT)

      *@       한도기준TE =한도사용액
               MOVE  XQJL0272-O-TE-LIMT-AUC(WK-I)
                 TO  XDJL4027-O-TE-LIMT-AUC1(WK-CUR-CNT)

           END-PERFORM
